module = collection of functions or definitions
packages = collection of modules

pypi = repo for the public modules
can download the module using = pip install module_name
to get the list of available modules - pip list

virtual env - to manage the different versions of a module in same machine for different projects
pip install virtualenv - to install venv module
python -m venv project1 - to craete a virtual environment for project1
source project1/bin/activate - to activate the environment
